"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-how-to-watch-paralympics-2024-free-tv-channel-live-stream-b1178446.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  TheParisParalympicsbegin today, offeringTeam GBmore chances to win medals this summer.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After a stunning Olympic Games in Paris, the action starts in the French capital following what promises to be another dramatic opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999326498732, \"rank\": 6.7350094951687e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9658079037627197, \"rank\": 0.013640965997840992, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Great Britain finished second at the delayed Tokyo Games last time out and have now been set a target of 100-140 medals by UK Sport.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9996237896175885, \"rank\": 0.00021269203246884568, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's everything you need to know about where to watch.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TV channel:The live action can be watched free-to-air in the UK on Channel 4, which has promised more than 1,300 hours of coverage.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6497603999271158, \"rank\": 0.5390284393178469, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The broadcaster is currently showing documentaries to pave the way and will be showing the coverage on television and online.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike at the Olympics, where the BBC had only limited broadcasting, Channel 4 will be showing every event with up to 18 streams accessible online.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9981131142971844, \"rank\": 0.000991081756186212, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will also be a nightly highlights show.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Live stream:Channel 4's website and app will provide a free live stream service online.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1140, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4\", \"score\": 0.9999880413091626, \"rank\": 1.1461690765308623e-05, \"text\": \"Channel 4\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Football  Arsenal: Jurrien Timber named in Netherlands squad ahead of Carabao Cup final amid Mikel Arteta update  Arsenal star named in squad ahead of Carabao Cup final  5  World  Iran missile attack on UK-US Diego Garcia military base raises fears London could be within striking distance  Iran fires ballistic missiles at UK-US base on Diego Garcia\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999775202232449, \"rank\": 1.1479819996878612e-05, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliza